Package powergrid.control

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IOHandler
    Handles basic I/O functions, such as writing and reading from files and moving or copying files.
    Mapper
    This class collects data from the RSBot environment and stores it in the singleton Grid-object.
    PathFinder
    This class deals with finding a path between two Points in the RSBot environment.
    ScriptLoader
    Loads a script by class name and executes it on the RSBot client.
    TaskManager
    Task Manager class for the entire plug-in.
    XMLToolBox
    Utility class providing methods for handling XML files
